LakeFeperd's Sonic The Hedgehog fan games &quot;Sonic Before The Sequel&quot;, &quot;Sonic Before The Sequel Aftermath&quot; and &quot;Sonic After The Sequel&quot; as well as MP3 and FLAC OSTs for both main games.

Sonic Before The Sequel 2012 &lt;a href=&quot;
https://sites.google.com/site/sonicbts/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
https://sites.google.com/site/sonicbts/&lt;/a&gt;

Sonic Before The Sequel Aftermath &lt;a href=&quot;
https://sites.google.com/site/sonicbts/aftermath&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
https://sites.google.com/site/sonicbts/aftermath&lt;/a&gt;

Sonic After The Sequel v1.1 &lt;a href=&quot;
https://sites.google.com/site/sonicbtsbooth/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
https://sites.google.com/site/sonicbtsbooth/&lt;/a&gt;

Sonic BTS is set between SEGA's Sonic the Hedgehog and Sonic 2 showing how the Death Egg was built. Sonic ATS then follows-on between Sonic 2 and Sonic and Knuckles detailing how the Death Egg crashes on Angel Island. BTS Aftermath is a &quot;side game&quot; between the two, with different game mechanics, meant as a bridge between them.

OSTs by Falk, Andy Tunstall, James Landino (KgZ), Funk Fiction, DJ Max-E, Mr Lange, and Li Xiao'an.
